 years.   "><span style="font-size:medium;"><br><br></span></span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px;"><span lang="ru"><span title="An ancient tree of &quot; Yama momo &quot; in front of the main hall has been standing here for more than 700 years.   "><span style="font-size:medium;">Уходя из храма, вы можете пройти по этой лесной тропинке. </span></span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px; text-align: start"><div style="text-align: center"><br><br></div><span lang="ru"><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:10pt; background-color: transparent"> </span><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7509%20%28420x315%29.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: large; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size:0in; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial" target=_blank><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1452596174725/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7509%20%28420x315%29.jpg?height=150&width=200" border="0" height="150px;" width="200px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"></span></a><span style="font-size:xx-small; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: transparent"> </span><span style="border-bottom-style: none; font-size: xx-small; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #551a8b; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size:0in; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial"><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7511%20%28420x315%29.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: large; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size:0in; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial" target=_blank><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1452596179261/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7511%20%28420x315%29.jpg?height=150&width=200" border="0" height="150px;" width="200px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"> </a></span><span style="font-size:xx-small; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif"> </span><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7517%20%28420x315%29.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:large; color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; background: none" target=_blank><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1452596198135/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7517%20%28420x315%29.jpg?height=150&width=200" border="0" height="150px;" width="200px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"> </span></a><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7521%20%28420x315%29.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:large; color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; background: none" target=_blank><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1452596203205/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7521%20%28420x315%29.jpg?height=148&width=200" border="0" height="148px;" width="200px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"> </span></a><span style="font-size:xx-small; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #551a8b"><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7522%20%28420x315%29.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; background: none" target=_blank><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1452596207350/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple-san-bao-si/CIMG7522%20%28420x315%29.jpg?height=150&width=200" border="0" height="150px;" width="200px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"></a></span></div><span title="An ancient tree of &quot; Yama momo &quot; in front of the main hall has been standing here for more than 700 years.   "><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:large;"><br><br></div></span><span title="Since the temple belongs to Nchiren sect, they also hold a ritual of &quot; Oeshiki &quot;."><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span title="Since the temple belongs to Nchiren sect, they also hold a ritual of &quot; Oeshiki &quot;." style="background-color: transparent">Поскольку храм принадлежит секте Nchiren, они также проводят ритуал &quot;Oeshiki&quot;. Особенное этого храма то</span><span title="What is sppecial about the temple is that they sereve radish as a traditional remedy to prevent paralysis.  " style="background-color: transparent">, что у них редис является  традиционном средством для предотвращения паралича.</span></span></div></span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px;"><br><br></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px; text-align: start"><div><div class="sites-embed-align-center-wrapping-off" style="clear: both; text-align: center; margin: 5px auto"><div class="sites-embed-border-off sites-embed" style="margin: 5px auto 0pt; border: 1px solid #a09681; font-size:12px; width:480px;"><div class="sites-embed-content sites-embed-type-youtube" style="text-align: left; overflow: hidden"></div></div></div></div><br><br></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px; text-align: start"><br><br></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px; text-align: start"><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:large; background-color: transparent">&#9660; Осень. 12 октября.</span></div><span lang="ru"><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:large; background-color: transparent"> </span></div><span style="font-size:medium;"><div style="text-align: center"><span title="Oeshiki-Daihoyo : It is common nation-wide to hold this type of ritual called Oeshiki-kai or Oeshiki-Daihoyo at temples of Nichiren sect on the evening of October 12th." style="background-color: transparent">Oeshiki-Daihoyo: Это общий общенациональный тип ритуала под названием Oeshiki-kai или Oeshiki-Daihoyo, проводится в храмах секты Nichiren 12 октября вечером. </span><span title="This is a memorial ritual of the day on which its great founder Nichiren Shonin passed away ( October 13th )." style="background-color: transparent">Это день памяти, в который его великий основатель Ничирен Шонин скончался (13 октября).</span><span title="Oeshiki = Anniversary of the death of the great Founder Nichiren Shonin.    " style="background-color: transparent">Oeshiki = годовщина смерти великого Основателя Ничирен Шонин.</span></div></span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px;"><span lang="ru"><span title="Oeshiki = Anniversary of the death of the great Founder Nichiren Shonin.    "><span style="font-size:medium;"><br><br></span></span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="background-color: transparent"> </span><span style="background-color: transparent">Во время этого ритуала Сутра Лотоса будет повторять в главном зале каждого храма.</span></span></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px;"><br></div><div style="font-family: Koulen, cursive; font-size:13px; text-align: start"><div style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size:small;"><div><div class="sites-embed-align-center-wrapping-off" style="clear: both; text-align: center; margin: 5px auto"><div class="sites-embed-border-off sites-embed sites-embed-full-width" style="margin: 5px auto 0pt; clear: both; width:888px; border: 1px solid #a09681; font-size:12px; font-family: Koulen, cursive !important"><div class="sites-embed-content sites-embed-type-map" style="text-align: left; overflow: hidden"></div></div></div></div><br><br></span><div style="font-size:13px;"><br><br></div></div><div style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Roboto, Arial; font-size:14px; white-space: nowrap; text-align: start">35°02&#39;06.6&quot;N 135°42&#39;04.7&quot;E</span></span></div><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent"><br></span></div><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent">&#12539;&#21517;&#31216;&#65306;&#19977;&#23542;&#23546;  &#65306;&#12306;616&#65293;8256  &#20140;&#37117;&#24066;&#21491;&#20140;&#21306;&#40180;&#28381;&#26494;&#26412;&#30010;32</span></div></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><br><br></div><div><div style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px; text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent">Автобус № 8 или поезд до станции Sanbouji-mae.</span><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent"> </span></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:medium;"><br><br></div></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><br></div><div><div><div style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:medium;"><div style="text-align: center; font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:large; color: #ffffff; background-color: #000000">  <span style="color: #ff0000">**</span> Святыня Фукуо-дзи <b>Fukuoji Shrine</b>  &#31119;&#29579;&#23376;&#31070;&#31038;&#12288; </span></div><div style="text-align: center; font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:xx-small;"> </span></div><div style="text-align: center">Тут находится захоронение императрицы Hanshi, матери императора <a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/88-temples-pilgrimage-hiking-around-ninnaji-yu-shi88ka-suo-xunri" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; background-color: transparent" target=_blank><b><span style="font-size:medium; color: #0066cc">Emperor Uda</span></b></a><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent"><b>.</b> </span></div><div style="text-align: center; font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:xx-small;"> </span></div></div><div><div style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><div style="text-align: center"><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sawanoike-pond-zeno-chi/img_0.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; font-size:13px; background: none" target=_blank><span style="font-size:medium;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1447377567325/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sawanoike-pond-zeno-chi/img_0.jpg?height=300&width=400" border="0" height="300px;" width="400px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"></span></a><span style="font-size:medium; background-color: transparent"> </span><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sawanoike-pond-zeno-chi/20140326000154.jpg?attredirects=0" rel="nofollow" style="color: #551a8b; border-bottom-style: none; font-size:13px; background: none" target=_blank><span style="font-size:medium;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1447377566575/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sagano-arashiyama/sawanoike-pond-zeno-chi/20140326000154.jpg?height=300&width=400" border="0" height="300px;" width="400px;" style="border: 0px; padding: 0px"></span></a></div><div><br><br></div></div><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size:medium; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif">На запад направление, вскоре после прохождения Ninnaji, вы придете к этому перекрестку. Это место называется Fukuoji &#31119; &#29579;&#23376; &#20132; &#24046;&#28857; Повернуть направо и следовать по оранжевой линии на дороге. Это шоссе маршрута 162. идет к северу. Если вы пойдете прямо, вы направитесь к области </span><a href="https://sites.google.com/site/futurememoriz/tgm-kyoto-guide/ukyo-ku-sagano-arashiyama" style="color: #551a8b; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px; background-color: transparent" target=_blank><b><span style="font-size:medium; color: #0066cc">Sagano</span></b></a><span style="font-size:medium; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: transparent">.</span></div><div style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.sanbouji-kyoto.or.jp/" rel="nofollow" style="font-size:large; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #551a8b" target=_blank>http://www.sanbouji-kyoto.or.jp/</a></div></div></div></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><br><br></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><br><br></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><b><a href="https://sites.google.com/site/futurememoriz/tgm-kyoto-guide/ukyo-ku-sagano-arashiyama/sanbouji-temple" target="_blank">sites.google.com/site/futurememoriz/tgm-kyoto-g...</a></b></div></div></div></div>
