                <div style='min-height:40px'><div align="center"><h3><br><br><span style="font-size:x-large; color: #f3f3f3; background-color: #783f04"><span style="font-family: 'trebuchet ms', sans-serif; background-color: #4c1130">Kitashirakawa Tenjin-gu Shrine  <span style="font-size:large;">&#21271;&#30333;&#24029;&#22825;&#31070;&#23470;</span></span></span><span id="sites-page-title" style="outline: none medium"></span><br><br><br><br></h3><span style="font-size:small; color: #ff0000"><b>Перейдите по этой ссылке, чтобы прочесть статью:</b></span></div><div align="center"><br><br></div><div align="center"><a href="https://sites.google.com/site/futurememoriz/tgm-kyoto-guide/kitashirakawa-tenji-gu-shrine" target="_blank">sites.google.com/site/futurememoriz/tgm-kyoto-g...</a></div><div align="center"><br><br><br><span style="font-size:xx-small;"> </span><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><a href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sakyo-ku/kitashirakawa-tenjin-gu-shrine-bei-bai-chuan-tian-shen-gong/kitashirakawa1.jpg?attredirects=0" target=_blank><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1450280939745/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sakyo-ku/kitashirakawa-tenjin-gu-shrine-bei-bai-chuan-tian-shen-gong/kitashirakawa1.jpg?height=419&width=625" style="width: 408px; height: 286px" border="0" height="419px;" width="625px;"></a>  </span><a style="text-align: left; font-size:medium;" href="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sakyo-ku/kitashirakawa-tenjin-gu-shrine-bei-bai-chuan-tian-shen-gong/CIMG6533.JPG?attredirects=0" target=_blank><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><img src="https://sites.google.com/a/transwordtgm.com/https-sites-google-com-a-transwordtgm-com-sites/_/rsrc/1450281291734/tgm-international/tgm-kyoto-guide/sakyo